  "display_name": "Big Data and Business Intelligence",
  "description": "This cluster of papers explores the impact of big data analytics on business performance, with a focus on supply chain management, predictive analytics, data science, and decision support systems. It delves into the challenges and opportunities of leveraging big data for firm performance and sustainability, as well as the integration of business intelligence and knowledge management. The research also examines the role of big data in innovation, risk mitigation, and operational transparency within organizations.",
